Package recipeTool

This package holds the essential classes of the RecipeTool application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Book
    This class contains all the recipes.
    Expiry
    This comparator is used to sort recipes according to their expiration dates.
    GUI
    This class holds the Graphical User Interface.
    RecipeTool
    This class is the starting point for application RecipeTool.
    Storage
    This class contains all the ingredients.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Segment
    This enum holds names for many UI components, so that they can be easily used in switch-statements.

Package recipeTool Description

This package holds the essential classes of the RecipeTool application. These classes are not designed to be re-usable in other projects.
